Module kivakit.core.kernel
Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.kernel.language.values.count

Class ConcurrentMutableCount

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.telenav.kivakit.core.kernel.language.values.count.ConcurrentMutableCount
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Receiver<Transmittable>, NamedObject, Countable, Listener, Transceiver
    public class ConcurrentMutableCount
extends java.lang.Object
implements Countable, Listener
    A mutable count value useful in lambdas and inner classes. Can be increment()ed, decrement()ed, added to with add(long) and add(long) and converted to different types with asCount() asInt() and asLong().
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
